headline: Golden Triangle Ventures Acquires Deep South Electrical Contractors in $4 Million Transaction
summary: Expanding over 600,000 square feet of active projects and strengthening the Company’s Construction DivisionAUSTIN, Texas, Oct. 08, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- via IBN – Golden Triangle Ventures, Inc. (OTC: GTVH), a diversified holding company focused on building and scaling high-growth operating businesses, today announced the acquisition of Deep South Electrical Contractors, a Texas-based industry leader generating between $6 million and $7 million in annual revenue and on track to surpass $10 mil

headline: Ulta Beauty (ULTA): Assessing Valuation After a Strong 8% Monthly Share Price Gain
summary: Ulta Beauty (ULTA) shares have been on investors’ radar as the stock delivered a strong month, climbing over 8%. With ongoing momentum and sustained interest in the beauty retailer, market watchers are assessing what could come next. See our latest analysis for Ulta Beauty. Ulta Beauty’s stock has maintained a bullish trend, with the latest share price at $556.77 after delivering a 17% gain over the past 90 days and a stellar 1-year total shareholder return of nearly 53%.
